# Links lychee should not check.
#
# The docs link check runs in OFFLINE mode (relative/local links only) so CI is
# deterministic and never flakes on an external host being slow or rate-limiting
# us. These patterns additionally exclude link shapes that are valid but not
# resolvable as local files:

# Shields.io / GitHub badge + status images (remote; skipped in offline mode
# anyway, listed here for clarity and for any future online run).
https://img.shields.io/.*
https://github.com/NikolayS/pg_bumpers/actions/.*

# Mail/anchor/templated links.
^mailto:
^#
